(183,	364,	'PEO - Electrica',	'peo-electrica',	'<div><strong>Los objetivos educacionales del programa:</strong></div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"margin-left:36pt;\">\r\n<p id=\"yui_3_13_0_ym1_1_1391090669206_2125\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p id=\"yui_3_13_0_ym1_1_1391564330811_2284\">1. Utilizar los conocimientos y habilidades de ingeniería para resolver problemas en la industria, promoviendo así su desarrollo tecnológico.</p>\r\n\r\n<p id=\"yui_3_13_0_ym1_1_1391564330811_2283\">2. Desarrollar y gestionar proyectos de desarrollo tecnológico, uniéndose a programas de postgrado, o la enseñanza.</p>\r\n\r\n<p id=\"yui_3_13_0_ym1_1_1391564330811_2282\">3. Demostrar competencia profesional de ingeniería para adaptar, mantener y aplicar las tecnologías emergentes y tradicionales según corresponda para mejorar su organización y la comunidad.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div><strong>The program educational objectives are:</strong></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"margin-left:18.15pt;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"margin-left:36pt;\">\r\n<p id=\"yui_3_13_0_ym1_1_1391090669206_2150\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p id=\"yui_3_13_0_ym1_1_1391564330811_2324\"><span id=\"yui_3_13_0_ym1_1_1391564330811_2323\">1.&nbsp; Use knowledge and engineering skills to solve problems in industry, thus promoting its technological development.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p id=\"yui_3_13_0_ym1_1_1391564330811_2326\"><span id=\"yui_3_13_0_ym1_1_1391564330811_2325\">2.&nbsp; Develop and manage technological development projects, joining graduate programs, or teaching.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p id=\"yui_3_13_0_ym1_1_1391564330811_2328\"><span id=\"yui_3_13_0_ym1_1_1391564330811_2327\">3.&nbsp; Demonstrate professional engineering competence to adapt, maintain, and implement emerging and traditional technologies as appropriate to improve their organization and community.</span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div><strong>Perfil Profesional de Egreso (PPE):</strong></div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"margin-left:36pt;\">1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Planear, diseñar, instalar y operar sistemas eléctricos de potencia, conforme a la normatividad nacional e internacional vigente.</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"margin-left:36pt;\">2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Planear, diseñar, instalar y operar sistemas de utilización de la energía eléctrica, con base en las normas de eficiencia energética.</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"margin-left:36pt;\">3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Planear, diseñar, instalar y operar sistemas de control y automatización, utilizando tecnología de punta.</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"margin-left:36pt;\">4.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Analizar, diagnosticar y presentar soluciones a problemas relacionados con la calidad de la energía eléctrica.</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"margin-left:36pt;\">5.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Participar en la administración y toma de decisiones de los recursos humanos, económicos y materiales en la ejecución de obras eléctricas.</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"margin-left:36pt;\">6.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Promover y aplicar las acciones necesarias relacionadas con el desarrollo sustentable de manera responsable, legal y ética.</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"margin-left:36pt;\">7.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Promover y realizar proyectos de investigación y desarrollo tecnológico.</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"margin-left:36pt;\">8.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Adaptar nuevas tecnologías en la mejora de los procesos industriales, equipos y obras eléctricas.</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"margin-left:36pt;\">9.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Probar, interpretar, diagnosticar y realizar mantenimiento de equipos e instalaciones eléctricas.</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"margin-left:36pt;\">10.&nbsp;Utilizar las nuevas tecnologías de la información y comunicación.</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"margin-left:36pt;\">11.&nbsp;Poseer una visión emprendedora realizando actividades de consultoría estableciendo su propia empresa para coadyuvar en el desarrollo de su entorno.</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"margin-left:36pt;\">12.&nbsp;Participar en equipos interdisciplinarios y multidisciplinarios.</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"margin-left:36pt;\">13.&nbsp;Fortalecer los valores individuales y colectivos a través de la comunicación.</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"margin-left:36pt;\">14.&nbsp;Fomentar el desarrollo de habilidades para una correcta y eficaz comunicación oral y escrita.</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"margin-left:36pt;\">15.&nbsp;Desarrollar habilidades gerenciales para impulsar el éxito de la empresa.</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"margin-left:36pt;\">16.&nbsp;Comprender su entorno político, económico, social y cultural.</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"margin-left:36pt;\">17.&nbsp;Crecer personalmente en todas sus dimensiones, adquiriendo conciencia de su propia identidad, sus aspiraciones y su propia identidad, sus aspiraciones y sus potencialidades.</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div><strong>Graduate’s Professional Profile:</strong></div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"margin-left:36pt;\">1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Plan, design, install and operate electric power systems, according to national and international regulations in force.</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"margin-left:36pt;\">2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Plan, design, install and operate systems using electric power, based on energy efficiency standards.</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"margin-left:36pt;\">3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Plan, design, install and operate control and automation systems, using cutting edge technology.</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"margin-left:36pt;\">4.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Analyze, diagnose and provide solutions to problems related to electrical power quality.</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"margin-left:36pt;\">5.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Participate in the management and decision making of human resources, economic and material in the execution of electrical works.</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"margin-left:36pt;\">6.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Promote and implement the necessary actions related to the development responsibly sustainable, legal and ethical.</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"margin-left:36pt;\">7.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;To promote and conduct research projects and technology development.</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"margin-left:36pt;\">8.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Adapting new technologies in improving industrial processes, equipment and electrical works.</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"margin-left:36pt;\">9.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Try, interpret, diagnose and perform maintenance of equipment and electrical installations.</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"margin-left:36pt;\">10.&nbsp;Using new information technologies and communication.</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"margin-left:36pt;\">11.&nbsp;Possessing an entrepreneurial vision carrying out consultancy establishing his own company to assist in the development of their environment.</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"margin-left:36pt;\">12.&nbsp;Participate in interdisciplinary and multidisciplinary teams.</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"margin-left:36pt;\">13.&nbsp;Strengthen individual and collective values ​​through communication.</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"margin-left:36pt;\">14.&nbsp;Foster the development of skills for proper and effective communication oral and written.</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"margin-left:36pt;\">15.&nbsp;Develop management skills to drive business success.</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"margin-left:36pt;\">16.&nbsp;Understanding the political, economic, social and cultural.</div>\r\n\r\n<p>Grow personally in every dimension, becoming aware of their own identity, its aspirations and its own identity, its aspirations and its potential</p>\r\n\r\n<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"width:0px;\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"width:140px;\">\r\n			<p><strong>